{"tid":1841234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔封關原因只有一個","createTime":"2020-01-25T07:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:20:59.000Z","uid":52596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eb7484c2a1c9f38bf3caa2ae8198342bfe3f4e03","tid":1841234,"uid":52596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"宜家武漢飛邊都被人遣返，但又唔係返武漢，變相助長咗傳播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦封咗城走唔到-&rsaquo;愈黎愈多人9衝去醫院-&rsaquo;醫院超荷淪陷-&rsaquo;集中唔到民眾仲散播到全中國-&rsaquo;成個中國疫情暴走，中共完全喪失管治能力-&rsaquo;中共既時代完結<br />\n<br />\n只要香港一日唔封關，就一直會有人湧入黎，起碼可以減輕上面既醫療負荷。<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係香港飛其他地方都唔會比人遣返（冇發燒的話）</span>成班有病撚樣實抱住走難心態飛去第度，香港變相幫手出口肺炎到全球各地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTL;DR：香港唔封關，全世界都奶硬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9381fd918d161597e5c37b9becdd33bb3b53fe49","tid":1841234,"uid":52596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母成班狗官根本不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d7b8adfcd8287245516a54d989710aa6c02d94","tid":1841234,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"高官要返大陸過年<br />\n封左返唔到香港 哽係say no<br />\n況且黑警都要上去叫雞"},{"pid":"0d02b0d6abb22c2dab7b5eb305e63458ae70d290","tid":1841234,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}